data.description: Motivated seller!! This charming home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 2 living areas where one could be an office space. The home sits on a spacious corner lot. The yard is HUGE and ready to plan your next year's garden. So, come and take a look for yourselves and see. Seller includes the dishwasher, stove, and built-in microwave. Only minutes to highway 183 and 161.  Near various restaurants and the shopping malls. All information contained herein deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer & buyer's agent to verify all information not limited to taxes, zoning, square footage, schools, acres, dimensions.
